{"tid":906372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全日空日航認更多機師醉駕 日航機師出茅招避檢測","createTime":"2018-11-18T02:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T02:56:54.000Z","uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50aa24b6b26da70f72665b4512eb16bd6767ccf5","tid":906372,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:45:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181117/58923832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58923832&d=xfmZOGnpSnlsLVliURnZaU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=996b182c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58923832&h=2dc15dcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181117/58923832</a><br />\n<br />\n日本航空公司機師執勤時醉酒的情況比預期嚴重，日航及全日空承認過去至少發生32宗機師酒精超標的事件，他們就事件道歉，承諾會改善問題。<br />\n<br />\n日航及全日空周五向國土交通省提交報告，交代最近有機師被揭發執勤時酒精超標的事件。兩家航空公司亦召開記者會向公眾致歉。日航承認共有24宗機師酒精超標的事件，包括來自同集團公司的機師，其中最嚴重者超標2.5倍。全日空在過去5年也有8宗同類事件。<br />\n<br />\n兩家航空公司均表示會致力確保機師自律，嚴守酒精攝取量。全日空計劃向機師分發流動酒精檢測器，日航就會為有醉酒問題的機師提供支援及指導。<br />\n<br />\n日航一名副機師10月28日在英國希斯路機場臨飛前被揭發體內酒精含量超出標準10倍，引起嘩然，副機師被英國當局拘捕。日航在提交的報告中表示，該名機師在進行內部酒精檢測時，並沒有真的向檢測儀器吹氣，蓄意規避，在場負責監察的兩名機長也承認疏失，並未確認副機師是否有正確向儀器吹氣。日航社長赤坂祐二表示︰「發生了絕不允許的事情，對此感到負有責任。」"},{"pid":"5197b33cf561a6cf2f31a2420194646c7d807723","tid":906372,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:51:36.000Z","msg":"都係搭番國泰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ffe3c8a1cc43a6695831cb698896d133233ed0","tid":906372,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:54:58.000Z","msg":"日本都咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d666ac5896c3f155cada4b48255a4354d3fe41c7","tid":906372,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:55:42.000Z","msg":"食女飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2539b514a5190e959a3d31b0e7572c2ac20b4c","tid":906372,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88ffe3c8a1cc43a6695831cb698896d133233ed0","tid":906372,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:54:58.000Z","msg":"日本都咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}